snippet.title: Community Inc Gameplay (No commentary, Adventure, PC game).
snippet.description:
Title: Community Inc Gameplay (PC game)
Genre: Indie, Simulation, Strategy
Developer: T4 Interactive
Publisher: tinyBuild 
Release Date: Summer 2017
Community Inc  In Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/631540/Community_Inc/
About Community Inc :
As a new Manager, build a happy community and trade with other races... for profit. Yes, that's right, we need their happiness so we can power up our portals. The Lings, your workers, will obey you and help you with your village. But beware, they can cause a lot of problems too. 
_ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ 
Steam Group VR: http://steamcommunity.com/groups/WorldVR
Steam Group Terror Horrror games: http://steamcommunity.com/groups/Terror_Horror_Games
Steam Group Love indies Games: http://steamcommunity.com/groups/LoveIndiesGames
_ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _
